version_description: All the other versions of Echosmith's - Cool Kids I've seen has been versions with only Capo on. My tab is with no Capo on. Also different chords, different from the ones with Capo on.
This version does not require a capo, it includes barre chords so it is rated intermediate. These are the exact chords used in the song. https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I9yguFRgEIY.
